| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2798 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0c3cad4a-eda3-5182-8fdb-a6a1ad25248a"
